<plot>By exploring the meaning of the garden in their lives, Canadian organic gardener Mary Perlmutter and her family members learn about themselves and each other. This film explores how the garden takes on various roles and functions within the lives of the family for whom it provides sustenance and enjoyment, including that of a mirror of the family itself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?010796</url></doc>
